snippet.title: Project S - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Project S is an open-world puzzle game where players can come together to explore a mysterious realm of logic and wisdom through either solo, co-op, or even large multiplayer game modes. Surrounded by floating islands, ancient architecture and awe-inspiring vistas, players will complete quests, find secrets and discover new puzzle islands, all while learning more about the origin and fate of this enigmatic universe. Project S is slated for launch in 2023.

#IGN #Gaming
